<H3><FONT face=Verdana size=2>Office Solutions</FONT></H3>
<P><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black"><FONT face=Verdana><FONT size=2>Today every office needs a broadband solution to do business. The office environment is often reliant on connectivity to the main office via the internet. The cost of a wide area network is incredibly high<SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman">. Your office may be located a short distance from a local wired internet feed but the cost to run a wire to your office is not in the budget, this is where Northern Wireless can help.</SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P><FONT face=Verdana>There are many technology choices for you to choose from. Let Northern Wireless take the complexity out of your decision making. With our proven experience we can guide you in the right direction. Why reinvent the wheel, we have the experience to set up your office with broadband integrating your existing equipment into a broadband wireless solution. We want to share our experience with you.</FONT></P>
<P><FONT face=Verdana>We recommend only and 802.11b (Wifi) and some 80211a standard equipment for outdoor network. These standards are developed by the IEEE, the same working groups that implemented Ethernet (802.3). We provide only Wifi certified equipment to ensure interoperability with all equipment in our solution. Wifi certified products is the most common and least expensive equipment on the market.</FONT></P>
